<div class="announcement-strip">
    <div class="container">
        <p class="announcement-text">
            <span class="short-text">Get Your $1 Shoutout — use code <span class="code-chip">SHOUTOUT</span> at checkout</span>
            <span class="long-text">We're inviting our first 100 businesses to join for just $1 — use code <span class="code-chip">SHOUTOUT</span> at checkout</span>
